      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-xl text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>LCP (Largest Contentful Paint):</strong> Main content loaded, target under 2.5s</li>
        <li><strong>FID (First Input Delay):</strong> Interactivity, target under 100ms</li>
        <li><strong>CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift):</strong> Visual stability, target under 0.1</li>
        <li><strong>Time to Interactive:</strong> Page fully functional, target under 3.8s</li>
        <li><strong>Total Blocking Time:</strong> JavaScript execution blocking, target under 200ms</li>
      </ul>
